{
  "chapter": 62,
  "chapter_summary": "四月十三日凌晨，陆小凤受老刀把子指派，化装成火工道人潜入武当后山。火工道人总管彭长备接应他，严厉告知山中规矩，并安排他睡在香积厨旁堆满腌萝卜的木屋中。陆小凤不堪忍受，溜出寻找食物，却被派往听竹小院送餐——那里住着精通易容术的少林名捕铁肩，处境极为危险。在听竹小院，陆小凤遇见王十袋、木道人、巴山小顾、花满楼等武林名宿，他们正在讨论西门吹雪与黑衣蒙面剑客之战，以及四个来历不明的老者。鹰眼老七识破陆小凤身份，与高行空前后封死退路。陆小凤以打赌为由施展金蝉脱壳之计逃脱，却被火工道人副总管长清截住，以巧计脱身后躲入武当大殿。掌门人石雁暗中替他掩护，陆小凤藏身横梁等待时机。然而彭长备被人用竹竿钉死灭口，大殿中九名火工道人也被神秘剑客一剑封喉全部杀害，凶手来去自如，身份成谜。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "带路人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你在这里等着，很快就会有人来接应你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中的人",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你来干什么的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来找豆子，十三颗豆子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "彭长备。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你喝过酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这里不准喝酒、不准说粗话、不准看女人，走路不准太快，说话不准太响。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "这里准不准放屁？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不知道你以前是干什么的，我也不想知道，到了这里，你就得守这里的规矩。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "还有一件事你最好也记住。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "到了山上，你就去蒙头大睡，千万不要跟人打交道，万一有人问起你，你就说是我找你来帮忙的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我的师弟长清是个很厉害的人，万一你遇上他，说话更要小心。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "我一定会很小心、很小心的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好，你跟我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你就睡在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "睡到什么时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "睡到我来找你的时候，反正这里有吃的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "吃这些腌萝卜？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "腌萝卜也是人吃的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只怕腌萝卜吃多了会放屁。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你可以不吃，就算饿一天，也饿不死人的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你还有什么不明白的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "只有一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "我只奇怪你为什么不改行做牢头去？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你过来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知不知道听竹小院里住的是什么人？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是少林铁肩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他若看出你易容改扮过，你就完了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "我能不能不去？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_chang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "彭长备",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为派给你这件差使的人，就是宋长清，他已经在注意你。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "西门吹雪说的是真话。能接得住他一轮快攻，绝不会超出三个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_shan_xiao_gu",
      "speaker_name": "巴山小顾",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "你也看不出那黑衣蒙面剑客的来历？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人的出手轻灵老练，功力极深，几乎已不在昔年老顾之下。最奇怪的是，他用的竟仿佛是武当剑法，却又比武当剑法更锋锐毒辣。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "你看他比你怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "text": "我这双手至少已有十年未曾握剑了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "你的手不会痒？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "text": "手痒的时候我就去拿棋子和酒杯。那不但比握剑轻松愉快，而且也安全得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "所以那天你就一直袖手旁观。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "text": "我只能袖手旁观，我手里不但有酒杯，还提着个酒壶。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "你说的那位以酒为命的朋友是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人据说是个告老还乡的京官，我看他却有点可疑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "可疑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他虽然尽量作出老迈颟顸的样子，其实脚下的功夫却很不弱，一跤从楼上跌下去，居然连一点事都没有，看他的样子，就像是我们一个熟人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "你看他像谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "text": "司空摘星。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那四个人非但功力都极深，而且路数也很接近。像那样的人，一个已很难找，那天却忽然同时出现了四个，简直就像是忽然从天上掉下来的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_xing_kong",
      "speaker_name": "高行空",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "更奇怪的是，他们的神情举动看来都差不多，就连面貌好像都有点相似，就好像是兄弟。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_jian",
      "speaker_name": "铁肩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟？像这样的兄弟，我只知道……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_tie_jian",
      "text": "你说的是虎豹兄弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算他们还在人世，也绝不会带着'满翠楼'的姑娘去喝酒的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "满翠楼的姑娘？你对这种事好像满内行的，你是不是也去过满翠楼？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "text": "我当然去过。只要有酒喝，什么地方我都去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_dai",
      "speaker_name": "王十袋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这老道说话的口气，简直就跟陆小凤一模一样。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "还有件事我更想不通。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个告老还乡的京官，怎么会忽然变成了火工道士？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "我好像输了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你输定了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "我生平跟别人打赌不下八百次，这一次输得最惨。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "打赌，赌什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "有个人跟我赌，只要我能在这屋里呆一盏茶功夫，还没有被人认出来，他就输给我一顿好酒，否则他从此都要叫我混蛋。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "跟你打赌的这个人是谁？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "他自己当然也是个混蛋，而且是个特大号的混蛋。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "陆小凤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他还没有死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "死人怎么会打赌？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他的人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还不进来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不能走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "text": "我为什么不能走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_yan_lao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鹰眼老七",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我想不通这件事，只有你能告诉我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_xing_kong",
      "speaker_name": "高行空",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错，他就是那位以酒为命的朋友，他怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "长清",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我不好，你更不好，我只要大叫一声，所有的人都会赶到这里来，就算你能一下子打倒我，也没有用。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chang_qing",
      "text": "你想怎么样？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "长清",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只想让你明白这一点。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chang_qing",
      "text": "我已经明白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "长清",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么你就最好让我把你抓住，以后对你也有好处。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chang_qing",
      "text": "好吧，反正我迟早总是逃不了的，倒不如索性卖个交情给你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_chang_qing",
      "text": "你下手轻一点好不好？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "长清",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "刚才有没有人进来过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yan",
      "speaker_name": "石雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yan",
      "speaker_name": "石雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里。我就是刚才进来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在想不通，这里又没有什么秘密，怎么会有奸细来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他是想来偷东西的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "偷我们这些穷道士？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫忘记这两天山上来的都是贵客。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他既不是小偷，也不是奸细。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是刺客！来刺那些贵客的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我们还没有抓住他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想他现在一定早就下山了，他又不是呆子，怎么会留在山上等死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倒楣的是长备，据说那个人是他带上山来的，现在十二连环坞的总瓢把子正亲自追问他的口供。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "报信人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彭长备死了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么死的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "报信人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二师叔他们正在问他口供时，外面忽然飞进了一根竹竿，活活的把他钉死在椅子上。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凶手抓住了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "报信人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有，太师祖已经带着二师叔他们追下去了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "长备死了，跟我们又没什么关系，你何必急着赶来报消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "报信人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟你虽然没关系，跟长慎师兄却有关系……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白了。长备死了，长清也受了罚，长慎师兄当然就变成了我们的总管，你是赶来报喜的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "火工道人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    }
